yingyinNormal.en: Thank you for dealing with an unfortunate situation. Now we can resume work on our new narrative without interference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常感谢你处理了这一不幸的事件，现在我们可以继续你的故事线而不受其它干扰了。

yingyinNormal.en: But in light of false stories over the last number of days about the state of our marriage, we now feel it's important to share this unfortunate news. Claire.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但鉴于这几天来关于我们婚姻状况的漫天谣传，我们现在认为只能说出这一不幸的消息，克莱尔。

yingyinNormal.en: This is most unfortunate, Captain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样很不好，船长。

yingyinNormal.en: My name's Devon. Well, that's unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我叫Devon。这才是不幸呢。

yingyinNormal.en: It's unfortunate that it has come to this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很遗憾，事已至此。

yingyinNormal.en: It's killed people, Henry. That's unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她杀了人，亨利。那真是不幸。

yingyinNormal.en: It's unfortunate that we meet under these circumstances.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很不幸，在这种情况下与你们相识。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi, we're here to be trained. I know. That's unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，我们是来受训的。我知道，很不幸。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm aware of the present situation of my unfortunate nephew.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我不幸外甥目前的状况。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it's unfortunate that my client got in the way of your car's progress.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是太可惜了，我的客户挡了你车的前途。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you should tell Peter. I did. He's still going. Oh, that's unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该告诉彼得。我告诉他了，他还是要去。那太不幸了。

yingyinNormal.en: You know? They just told an unfortunate lie to deal with a difficult situation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你明白吗？他们只是为了摆脱困境而撒了个很糟的谎。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you for coming. I'm sorry for how everything has worked out. It's unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多谢前来。我很遗憾事情闹成这样，太不幸了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Safir, thank you so much for coming. I'm so sorry about this unfortunate situation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 萨菲尔先生，谢谢你能过来，很抱歉弄得这么尴尬。

yingyinNormal.en: A precious few people know about your true identity. It would be unfortunate if we forgot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没什么人知道你的真实身份，要是我们不小心忘了就惨了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm gonna do the best I can. Unfortunate, I wasn't blessed with luscious lashes like some of you all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会尽自己最大努力去涂，悲剧的是，我没有茂盛的睫毛。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't say that. Ms. Searle's injury is unfortunate, but it has nothing whatever to do with my car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有这么说，瑟尔女士受伤是很不幸，可是她受伤和我的车没关系。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, I lost that key chain years ago. Really? Did you look under things? Well, that is unfortunate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿…我的钥匙串早就丢了。真的吗？你有没有到处翻翻找找？真是太不幸了。

yingyinNormal.en: I suffered an unfortunate series of embarrassing incidents. I just want a wine bath and to go to sleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不幸遭遇了一连串尴尬事件。我只想喝点小酒泡个澡去睡觉。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I am scary. Sorry, the lightning. Lightning was an unfortunate coincidence. You look lovely, lovely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很抱歉。我很吓人吗？不，是闪电，刚才的闪电，真是很不巧，你很漂亮，你真的很漂亮。
